text.jpText:
――おし！　ウマスタ、フォローした！
フォロワーにウチいるっしょ？
text.enText:
―Oshi! Umasta, I follow you! 
You follow us, don't you?

text.jpText:
そうそれ！　6万8320フォローのやつ！
え、なにそのビビり顔！　ウケる！
text.enText:
Yes that's it! The one with 68,320 followers! 
What's with the scared face! That's hilarious!

text.jpText:
気になんのフォロってバしてたら爆増えてさ！
TL、激流でやべーケド！
その分、飽きないんだよね～♪
text.enText:
I've been following some people I'm 
interested in, and the number of followers 
has been increasing! My TL is a torrent! 
That's why I can't get enough of it!

text.jpText:
ウチ、ハートしまくっから！
たのちーポストよろ～☆
text.enText: I'll be hearted all the way! Please post!
